reviewText: This dvd is a wonderful, inspiring, worship video. The audio is fantastic and addictive~ I will put it on and then do my housework, singing along. The video/visual aspect is also great. I highly recommend this dvd if you like Hillsong at all or if you enjoy worship/praise music. I was not a big Hillsong fan, but LOVE this dvd. It is one that the more I listen to it the more I enjoy it.
